          WT: 0.5 &nbsp;Size: MEDIUM<br>
          Class: WIZ MAG ENC<br>
          Race: HUM</font></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      </center>
    </div>
  </blockquote>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p><font size="2">You say, 'I want to craft a gloves'<br>
    <br>
    Shana Liskia says 'Gloves are very important for your early training 
    especially Gemdiver. While you are learning your first set of incantations 
    you should not have to worry about any injuries to your hands. To create 
    your glove material you will need to combine 3 Woven Spider Silks, 1 Giant 
    Scarab Brain, 1 High Quality Cat Pelt 1 Zombie Skin and 1 Large Leaf Scarab 
    Leg in your assembly kit. Once you have created the proper material take it 
    to a loom along with this mold to fashion your very own Arcane Scientists 
    Gloves.'</font></p>
  <blockquote>
    <div align="center">
      <center>
