    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p><font size="2">You say, 'I want to craft a sleeves'<br>
    <br>
    Shana Liskia says 'Sleeves will be a great and necessary addition to your 
    armor. To create your sleeve material you will need to combine 2 Woven 
    Spider Silks, 2 Bone Chips, 1 Spider Legs and Cloth Sleeves in your assembly 
    kit. Once you have created the proper material take it to a loom along with 
    this mold to fashion your very own Arcane Scientists Sleeves.'</font></p>
  <blockquote>
    <div align="center">
      <center>
