    <p><font size="2"><br>
    <br>
    You say, 'I want to craft a trousers'<br>
    <br>
    Shana Liskia says 'I would always recommend pants to all my new students 
    since they are a very important part of your armor set. To create your 
    trouser material you will need to combine 4 Woven Spider Silks, 1 Embalming 
    Dust, 1 Rotting Zombie Skull and 1 Armadillo Tail in your assembly kit. Once 
    you have created the proper material take it to a loom along with this mold 
    to fashion your very own Arcane Scientists Trousers.'</font></p>
  <blockquote>
    <div align="center">
