    <p><font size="2"><br>
    <br>
    You say, 'what final assignment'<br>
    <br>
    Shana Liskia says 'I have a trinket that was given to me by my mother a long 
    time ago. Before she died I told her I would always keep it close to me. 
    Recently, some militia officers came in to our academy and confiscated 
    anything that appeared to be valuable. Fearing for my life I did not fight 
    to keep the necklace my mother gave me. The officer that took it was named 
    Teridsan. If you should find him you have my permission to kill him if 
    that's what it takes to get my necklace back. Return to me when you have my 
    necklace along with 2 Lion Teeth.'</font></p>
